<sect2 id="plot_data">
<title>Plot Data</title>
<para>
The <guimenuitem>Plot Data</guimenuitem> dialog allows you to plot some information about elements. The X-axis represents a range of elements (from one number to a higher number). You set this range using the First Element and Last Element fields on the dialog. The display does not change until you click on the <guibutton>Plot</guibutton> button.
</para>
<screenshot>
<mediaobject>
<imageobject>
